snippet.title: Security Breach: The Remains Gameplay Trailer #1
snippet.description:
JOIN THE DISCORD SERVER TO KEEP UPDATED, GET EXCLUSIVE TEASERS, AND VOTE ON WHAT YOU WANT IN REMAINS -  https://discord.gg/fxdyB2z2E9

Link Tree! - https://linktr.ee/RemainsDevTeam

Game Banana! - https://gamebanana.com/wips/79290

Remains Twitter! - https://twitter.com/TheRemainsSB

We hope you enjoyed the show! Freddy and the gang are pretty tired so they'll be out for a while! We hope you enjoy just a brief glimpse, of what remains.

The Remains is a soon to be releasing mod for Steel Wool Studios' Five Nights at Freddy's Security Breach. This mod restores every single scrapped mission, model, map, minigame, ETC. Back into full functioning order!  It will be free to download/play and available on several sites once released! We hope you enjoyed this trailer and we hope that we can deliver a great product for you all!
